From: KOSHIKAWA Kenichi <reishoku.misc@pm.me>
Date: 2026-01-28
Subject: rpmdev-spectool: add -v alias for --version

help2man invokes rpmdev-spectool with -v; argparse previously rejected
it, causing manpage generation to fail during build.

---
 rpmdev-spectool | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

--- a/rpmdev-spectool
+++ b/rpmdev-spectool
@@ -77,6 +77,7 @@ def get_args() -> dict:
     ops.add_argument(
         "--version",
         "-V",
+        "-v",
         action="version",
         version="%(prog)s {}".format(__version__),
         help="Print the version and exit",
